Remote_Title_ReviewAllatOnce_Tutorial_Po: About the “Review All at Once” Function

You can use the “Review All at Once” function
when you sync multiple sleep data entries
from another device, such as Pokémon GO
Plus +. You can see the results of multiple sleep
sessions together without going through sleep
research for each one. Please note that if you
sync three or more sleep data entries at the
same time, the “Review All at Once” function
will automatically be used on all entries except
for the most recent one.
